snippet.title: Asteroid Redirect Mission Playthrough
snippet.description:
Join us on our mission to redirect an asteroid inside Kerbal Space Program! The Asteroid Redirect Mission was made in collaboration with NASA. Coming soon.

You can read the the most discussed questions about the ARM here: http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/content/265-Kerbal-Space-Program-Asteroid-Redirect-Mission-The-FAQ

For more information about the NASA Asteroid Initiative visit this link http://www.nasa.gov/asteroidinitiative

http://www.kerbalspaceprogram.com
